Restaurant Review: Sentiment Analysis & Word of Bag Analysis:

Perform analysis on the restaurant review posted on zomato, for improvement in operations & serving pattern,
post analysis operator contacted customers to enhance their experience and revised review to increase rating on the aggregator site.

Process:
Reviews Extractions from Aggregator Site | Data Cleaning | Convert to Dataframe | Create Corpus |
Convert to Document Term Matrix |  Save DTM to Dataset Conversion | Merge Dataset | Apply Classifier | Apply Confusion 
Matrix | Run Sentiment Analysis
